name: Delicious Nod-Krai Hot Dog
desc: Classic convenience food. Freshly cooked sausage paired with freshly baked bread. With each bite, the irresistible aroma of fat fills the palate. It's gone in a few quick bites, leaving you craving another.

value.text: Increases all party members' CRIT Rate by 12% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
